description: Battle of the defeated. One wrestler is going to walk away with her first US win. The other is getting fucked on the mat.. again. The Gymnast is lean, ripped and strong. The Blond Giant is flexible and determined to win her first match against an equally skilled opponent. Who will get her first win here at US?
title: The Gymnast (Lifetime 0-2) vs. The Blond Giant (Lifetime 0-1)
